        <t:profileDesc xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
            <t:creation/>
            <t:abstract>
                <t:p>
                    The so-called β-recension of the Ethiopic Physiologus. The text displays a rewriting or, in some cases, even a deep reworking in the course of the transmission history. 
                    The chapter numbering is rearranged as compared to the Greek, and counts 57 chapters.
                </t:p>
            </t:abstract>
